title: The Amazing Kaylee and the Hunt for the Eggnapper
description: Kaylee returns for another exciting adventure! Now that she and her friends found her missing Furmaid, life at the farm began to return to normal. Until one morning, there was big news coming from the chicken coop! Overnight, one dozen (that is twelve) eggs were missing! Who is the Eggnapper? Will Kaylee and her friends solve the mystery and bring the eggs back home? Join Kaylee on another journey around the magical, mystical valley as she meets new friends and sees old ones too, and helps find those eggs!
author: Daniel Morris
